{"tid":172561,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"回覆提醒功能實作建議","createTime":"2017-03-26T03:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T03:58:33.000Z","uid":84136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd01cec84cc8ef13ad5d632f8238bdb99d7322a6","tid":172561,"uid":84136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"係sidebar新增「追post」模組（類似「留名」）<br />\n開post+回覆<span style=\"color: gold;\">預設</span>會將該討論加入「追post」列表<br />\n（會員回覆時可以選擇不追蹤，亦可以隨時係「追post」列表移除）<br />\n<br />\n每當有人回覆時，business logic如下:<br />\n//insert comment to post(say x)<br />\nSELECT DISTINCT user_id<br />\nFROM comment<br />\nWHERE post_id=x<br />\n如是者你得到該post所有回覆者<br />\nif(user.follow.x) {<br />\n    Update 「追post」列表<br />\n    admin bot以PM功能通知user<br />\n}<br />\n<br />\n結果illustration <br />\n<img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ef3de6cd263bff79dfd5a31bf4b79edf389fb324/687474703a2f2f7777772e6d6178696d697a6575726d61632e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031332f30392f312e6a7067\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcamo.githubusercontent.com%2Fef3de6cd263bff79dfd5a31bf4b79edf389fb324%2F687474703a2f2f7777772e6d6178696d697a6575726d61632e636f6d2f77702d636f6e74656e742f75706c6f6164732f323031332f30392f312e6a7067&h=081d6f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1999"},{"pid":"60a7d65406396d361072dfa0cd6a7dbc7321e939","tid":172561,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2499bb01ad09486cf6a6256c83dc35a0fc5818c1","tid":172561,"uid":84136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4465d8f8aa049f4a6b4270e3a2cfa1d5c92a75","tid":172561,"uid":27718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":